    "description": {
      "value": "<p>As a Magic action, you can reach into your @UUID[Compendium.materia-dnd.class-and-subclass-features.Item.JT7RobJSiQVCO1dh]{Alchemist's Satchel} and pull out a stick that produces a thick plume of smoke. You can hold on to the stick or throw it to a point up to 30 feet away as part of the action used to produce it. The area in a 10-foot radius around the stick is filled with thick smoke that blocks vision, including Darkvision. The stick and smoke persist for 1 minute and then disappear. Even strong winds will not disperse the smoke.</p>",
